title: Love Where You Live only at Midtown Square!
posting_body: ['Midtown Square', '2301 E Union St, Seattle, WA, 98122', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 187', 'Welcome to Midtown Square at 23rd & Union in Seattle', 'Studio, 1 Bath', 'A historic, central Seattle crossroad, 23rd & Union will always be an intersection of life in all of its splendid forms.', 'From the vibrant artwork to the carefully selected commercial tenants to the residential spaces, Midtown Square was designed for — and by — the Central Area community.', 'This unique development adds a wide variety of apartment homes (30% of which are designated as affordable units per City of Seattle guidelines), along with new retail space for local, minority-owned businesses, all within a massive, cultural artwork-focused public square for all to enjoy.', 'Midtown Square offers new opportunities within a space that regards the past with respect, honors the present with dignity, and gives inspiration to the future.', 'Features', '- Townhouse units', '- Studio, one, and two bedroom units', '- New unique development', '- Affordable options', 'Community Amenities', '- Parking garage', '- Elevators', '- Central Area community', '- Courtyard', '- Roof deck', '- Package storage', '- On-site retail', '- Bike room', '- Cultural artwork-focused public square', '- Vibrant artwork', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 1pm to 4pm', 'Saturday: 9:30AM to 3:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats and Dogs allowed', '**', 'Restricted breeds apply***', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'LEzGVff7Q7vS']
